I get frustrated trying to buy the kind of ass toys that fit easily up my butt,
(they're all either too fat or too thin, too long or too short) and also to
find special-purpose ones to fulfil certain of the fantasies my overworked
imagination dreams up for me <g>.

My solution has been to make my own custom-sized butt toys.  Apart from the
obvious advantage of custom sizing, they're cheap, and you can make lots of
different ones for different purposes.  I've made two butt plugs, a dildo and
two "tails" so far and I intend to make one with a tube down the middle and a
funnel on the outside end so that Daddy can pour whatever he likes into my ass
(or my mouth if he puts it in that end) and I have other ideas too.

The basic materials are moulded foam pipe insulation (the kind that comes in 3
foot lengths with a hole down the middle - to put on hot water pipes), PVC
electrical tape (insulating tape to Brits) and a kind of liquid rubber stuff
called "Plasti-Dip" which is used for putting a rubber/plastic coating on the
outside of things like tool handles.  Available here in Canada from good tool
shops like Lee Valley Tools, but it's made in the US.

Method is -
1.  cut yourself a suitable length of foam - you probably know what's a
    good length for you, and if you don't, err on the short side (4" or so) to
    start with. You can always make longer ones later.
2.  Round off one end roughly with scissors
3.  Put something in the hole at the other end of the foam to act as a
    stiffener and stop the toy from sliding in too far (eg a _short_ wooden
    dowel of the appropriate size with a flat piece of wood attached across one
    end). Make sure you don't use anything which could puncture the foam and
    injure you.
4.  Wrap the whole thing tightly and thoroughly with several layers of tape.
    I found it best to start in the middle and work towards the tip, stopping
    once had the foam bent inwards to a nice rounded point. Then I placed
    several short lengths of tape across the tip and back along the length. The
    start just back of the tip and wind over the short lengths and along to the
    back end.  Wrapping the back end is a bit awkward and takes some fiddling.
    When you finish the last wrap, don't stretch the end of the tape too much
    as you stick it down - it will creep backwards under the plastic coating
    and rip it.
5.  Use the plasti-dip to coat the outside with a continuous smooth layer. This
    takes several coats and you will probably have to do one end, then the
    other end, overlapping in the middle, and back to the first end again.

"Tails" made by this method are a lot of fun - I made one which has vinyl
flogger tails hanging out of the plug section & which hang out of my ass when
I'm wearing it - very useful, Daddy can whip it out and whack me with it if the
mood strikes. It's quite amusing for onlookers if I swing my butt from side to
side because the tails start swinging too, and whacking me - unfortunately on
the upper thighs instead of the ass.  The other has heavy chain hanging out of
it.  Just make sure that the sections which will be in your ass are smooth and
coated with the rubber so they can't do any damage. You also need something to
stop it from continuing to work its way deeper into your ass - a crossbar of
some kind.

There are two sizes of the foam, for 1/2" pipe and 3/4" pipe. I used the 1/2"
size and found it perfect once it was bound up with tape. YMMV. The foam is
also useful for other things, eg covering sling suspension chains if they're
too noisy, or covering something to be used as a bit or gag in the mouth. You
could even use it to insulate your hot water pipes if you're really stuck for a
use for the bits you have left over <g>.

Kevin


