photos, most of which are about mayhem, but there's a very strange collection
at the start of the book of a woman forcing another into a very painful-looking
harness in order to pull a buggy...  All the photos, relevant to this list or 
not are beautifully chosen and laid out.  I was just so happy to find this that
I thought I'd share the find, as there seem to be a lot of bookish people on
this list.
